# The bot (bot.py) needs NO keys. The dashboard and hourly cloud run are free.
#
# The "ask your data" tool (ask.py) also works with NO key at all (free summary mode).
# To get fluent AI-written answers, add ONE of the keys below — then copy this
# file to ".env" and paste your key.

# ---- Option A: FREE — Google Gemini (recommended; no card, no money) ----
# Get a free key at:  https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.0-flash      # optional override

# ---- Option B: Paid — Anthropic Claude (optional, pennies per question) ----
# Get a key at:  https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ASK_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8          # optional: most capable, pricier than Haiku
